name: Descending from Myr 03
description:
This collection of 10 limited pieces will follow the journey of Kispilak, who stole compassion from Myr to give it back to nature. 

The mazes auto-destroy and reconstruct each hour in a completely randomized process, regardless if somebody is crossing them at the time. 

Will he make it?
